# Architecture

- Next.js App Router with Route Handlers for API
- PostgreSQL + Prisma for data
- Auth.js database sessions
- Cloudflare R2 for images (presigned upload)
- pg-boss worker on Render for async jobs
- Feature modules under `src/features/` and domain logic under `src/server/services/`
